{"tid":351140,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[品蠔]召喚連登所有鍾意食生蠔既面孔","createTime":"2017-08-07T18:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T21:32:01.000Z","uid":34259,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79d606872556eb675673915d7dfce67ce3003609","tid":351140,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T18:15:27.000Z","msg":"自從去過日本食過靚蠔就愛上左生蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附上肥蠔兩隻<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6REC1HQl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6REC1HQl.jpg&h=a178d7cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放入個口度浪下浪下，<br />\n一咬落去咇曬D汁出黎，個刻先知咩叫鮮嫰多汁<br />\n<img src=\"https://i3.read01.com/uploads/0Fcbze6Lc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi3.read01.com%2Fuploads%2F0Fcbze6Lc8.jpg&h=a010165a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再啜埋殼入面咸咸地既海水，<br />\n合埋眼個陣成個人就好似係海入面咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://read.html5.qq.com/image?src=forum&amp;q=5&amp;r=0&amp;imgflag=7&amp;imageUrl=mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/WCQSu8LEZ0RWyDv5OiciayjFALyp3CqRqJfcIoz7C3INbVhEibtyjCFA78DBoaA2cuaHcAZqvVqNhsmZyvOxrukaQ/0?wx_fmt=gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fread.html5.qq.com%2Fimage%3Fsrc%3Dforum%26q%3D5%26r%3D0%26imgflag%3D7%26imageUrl%3Dmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FWCQSu8LEZ0RWyDv5OiciayjFALyp3CqRqJfcIoz7C3INbVhEibtyjCFA78DBoaA2cuaHcAZqvVqNhsmZyvOxrukaQ%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif&h=e876822a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後再飲返啖生啤，人生一大樂事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我講咁多廢話只係想搵同好，分享下香港有咩地方食到靚蠔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b73d1fe0bb2595b147751d6028017fc11817fa9","tid":351140,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T19:34:20.000Z","msg":"蠔 淨係個樣已經好正<br />\n<br />\n要求唔高，點食最抵？"},{"pid":"0b1ab8d3dfb7d32a374932eec78e639e9328a1c6","tid":351140,"ui