/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n酒店自助餐果啲真係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444262195c5270d006e8a02311cc096ee899c9e5","tid":351140,"uid":74438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T01:24:55.000Z","msg":"香港食蠔應該係去D賣高級食材既鋪頭最抵架啦 質素又好 例如：ocean three , season wine個類鋪頭<br />\n利申：非打手"},{"pid":"3daf3ebe4fa54e43e744c41d747489e2111304c9","tid":351140,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名學食蠔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得好臭，要落勁多辣椒醬先食到，點搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無論魚生定蠔，都鍾意就咁食⼃⼁"},{"pid":"753252c9bb28623e9f78d4a91601ea8ac907b63f","tid":351140,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名學食蠔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得好臭，要落勁多辣椒醬先食到，點搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我無論魚生定蠔，都鍾意就咁食佢原汁原味，咩都唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ⼁</blockquote>"},{"pid":"df3c6f71bf07e249d804bc6dc80aa00e37976eb8","tid":351140,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:13:20.000Z","msg":"做過ocean 3 有人想知再講"},{"pid":"9cb364d9f5d69c6dfc7040f6f9716105287d7605","tid":351140,"uid":2671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"覺得陣味好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b361ae4903b5ebb2fd5221508eff3856f1c14a","tid":351140,"uid":89432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T02:15:37.000Z","ms