ile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3620febf5f73aff34dce408c761e9af6d1aad8","tid":351140,"uid":51328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:19:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/111947_7badb0f4a7418e17a81f9db2084cdba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F111947_7badb0f4a7418e17a81f9db2084cdba1.jpg&h=1543415b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fabee2663267488a91eacbf2d88ab8510a72f7e7","tid":351140,"uid":109738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:24:39.000Z","msg":"每次食都唔會記得啲法文名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6aed6a27689ac9afe4852da1280cd6187f4542e","tid":351140,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/111947_7badb0f4a7418e17a81f9db2084cdba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F111947_7badb0f4a7418e17a81f9db2084cdba1.jpg&h=1543415b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7a78937fc4baa98a0174e92b1270a2ff13e36af","tid":351140,"uid":34259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/08/111947_7badb0f4a7418e17a81f9db2084cdba1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F08%2F111947_7badb0f4a7418e17a81f9db2084cdba1.jpg&h=1543415b&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji